      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "3.4. Data Migration",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For existing users with the deprecated \u201cClient corrections\u201d role, assign both new roles  to preserve functionality, "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "or",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " perform a manual audit and distribute them to the appropriate new roles based on their responsibilities."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tech notes",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "1. Create new endpoints in wallet credit correction  and debit correction."
          },
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "2. Check amount under 0 in new endpoints."
          },
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "3. Use new endpoint in BO. Use permission service."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "4. Separate "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "/perform",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " endpoint in wallet into two for credit/debit with keeping same implementation, to be able to add permissions check to request url via management gateway, or try approach with keeping original endpoint, and on gateway level route request from credit/debit operations to "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "/perform",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " endpoint in wallet."
          },
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "5. 2step migration. 1 - Migration to add new permissions, and add new permissions for all roles which had old singular permission. 2 - After release, create migration to delete old singular permission"
          },
          {
            "type": "hardBreak"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "6. No need to update platform permissions, only new permission service with new approach with determining permissions by request url."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
